name: THE UNNATURAL 6
description:
Meet Del Vi, a jazzy fiend from the depths of hell. He is looking to dominate the uncultured puny humans with the sinful, vibrant noise of JAZZ. He's currently a one-demon band (with the help of his loyal roadie) so he must venture topside and seduce 5 extra humans to form THE UNNATURAL SIX and have their big debut at THE HOUSE OF STYX.

//CREATED DURING UCF's GAMEDEV KNIGHTS SPOOKY GAME JAM 2021
